    "body": "And you may already know this, but if you want to date math confirming to a frequency, you add the actual offsets themselves:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nIn [187]: index + pd.offsets.BDay()\r\nOut[187]: DatetimeIndex(['2012-01-06', '2012-01-09', '2012-01-10', '2012-01-11'], dtype='datetime64[ns]', freq='B')\r\n```"
